mpdris2 (0.9.2~rc1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * First release candidate for 0.9.2 on the b0bbywan/mpDris2 fork
  * Cover art improvements: fetch from MPD via readpicture/albumart commands
  * CUE/cdda cover art fallback via MPD database search
  * Add ConditionUser guards to systemd unit (folded in)
  * Initial Debian packaging for the b0bbywan APT repository,
    based on Simon McVittie's official Debian packaging

